-- Corcoran Says `Handling Rejection' Is Key to Success (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2012-08-07T15:34:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-07/corcoran-says-handling-rejection-is-key-to-success-audio-.html
Barbara Corcoran, the founder and 
former chairman of the Corcoran Group and author of "Shark 
Tales," says learning to "handle rejection" has been the key to 
much of her success in business. Corcoran talked to Bloomberg's 
Vonnie Quinn and Kathhleen Hays on "The Hays Advantage" in a pre
recorded interview which aired on Bloomberg Radio on August 6, 
2012.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 19:30
 